dc_title_s: Genoese world map, 1457, facsimile and critical text incorporating in free translation the studies of Professor Theobald Fischer.
dc_description_s: 5 p. 1., 66 p., 1 l.: ill., 5 maps (incl. front.) This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
